{
  "stem": "16442.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And unfortunately, they explained it to me and to my brother that things are not as good as they used to be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I enjoyed sports and-- all kinds of sports what my mother taught me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then later on when things were really tough, you know, I tried to help my mother in the business, give her a hand because it was hard for Jewish people to get help.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was about all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I remember-- the beautiful table set for Friday night and waiting for my father to come home to make kiddush and have the special food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always had special food what we did not have during the week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, I positively remember the feeling of Erev Yom Kippur, when the family got dressed special and we all went together to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very special feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was quite an excitement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to empty all our pockets from our clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to take all our books outside and air them [? for ?] God forbid should be any crumbs in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was cooking and baking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Passover always had a special smell in the house, the clean smell, and the special foods which we ate only Passover.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, of course, we had a beautiful Seder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The table was set.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when things were getting tough, my father used to come home from the synagogue and always brought quite a few people to our table.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people were people who escaped, smuggled through the border from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because things were bad already there, we heard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were sort of getting people together, and they tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we felt terrible for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
